des: Spume FM is all about capturing the heart and soul of Cornwall’s coastal vibe, mixing the thrill of surf culture with the pulse of killer tunes and epic times. It’s like the rush of catching the perfect wave, with a soundtrack that flows as naturally as the swell at Fistral Beach. Sun-drenched days, sandy feet, and the constant rhythm of the ocean—each beat paired with tracks that keep the energy high and the vibes even higher. Spume FM isn’t just a radio station; it’s the soundtrack to your best times in Cornwall, whether here year round or visiting, where the music is always on point, the drinks are always cold, and the atmosphere is charged with a laid-back yet totally rad edge.
